  <item>
    <title>bash, zsh</title>
    <link>http://lumiere.ens.fr/~guerry/20221215113855-sdkman.html#orge907a71</link>
    <author>7696122 at gmail dot com (nil)</author>
    <guid isPermaLink="false">http://lumiere.ens.fr/~guerry/20221215113855-sdkman.html#orge907a71</guid>
    <pubDate>Sun, 25 Dec 2022 06:41:00 +0900</pubDate>

    <description><![CDATA[<div class="org-src-container">
    <pre class="src src-sh">curl -s <span style="color: #8b2252;">"https://get.sdkman.io"</span> | bash
    </pre>
    </div>

    <p>
    위 명령으로 .bash_profile .zshrc 생성됨
    </p>

    <p>
    .bash_profile .zshrc created by the above command
    </p>

    <div class="org-src-container">
    <pre class="src src-bash">source <span style="color: #8b2252;">"$HOME/.sdkman/bin/sdkman-init.sh"</span>
    </pre>
    </div>
    ]]></description>
  </item>

